<plot>Mike and Shawn were a happy couple until, after a night of partying, their lives were changed forever by senseless violence. Brutally attacked for being gay, Mike is put in the hospital in critical condition. Shawn, left mourning by his side and feeling helpless, is presented with a decision to take action against those who hurt Mike. Explores the repercussions of a hate crime and asks who, no matter how much they may feel justified in doing so, has the moral authority to take matters into their own hands.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?489585</url></doc>
